  "prompt": "I cleared the muApt 2016 test. How can I prepare for the remaining rounds?",
  "response": "Congratulations on clearing the MuAFT 2016 test! To prepare for the remaining rounds, here are some steps you can take:\n\n1. Interview Preparation:\n- Review common interview questions\n- Practice mock interviews\n- Research the organization thoroughly\n- Prepare answers highlighting your strengths\n- Work on your communication skills\n\n2. Group Discussion (if applicable):\n- Stay updated on current affairs\n- Practice group discussion skills\n- Work on your communication and presentation abilities\n- Learn to balance assertiveness with listening skills\n\n3. Document Verification:\n- Organize all necessary documents\n- Ensure all certificates are original and properly authenticated\n- Keep copies of educational and professional documents ready\n\n4. Physical Fitness Test (if required):\n- Follow a structured fitness training program\n- Focus on endurance, strength, and flexibility\n- Practice specific physical fitness tests\n- Maintain a healthy diet\n\n5. Medical Examination:\n- Get a comprehensive health check-up\n- Maintain good health and fitness\n- Address any existing medical conditions\n\n6. Additional Preparation:\n- Stay confident and positive\n- Continue studying relevant subjects\n- Keep improving your general knowledge\n- Practice time management\n\nIf you need more specific guidance, consider consulting previous candidates or official MuAFT resources.",
